<i>noun</i>: 트림 [트ː림] <i>verb</i>: 트림하다 [트ː림하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>트림 [트ː림]</dt><br>
<dd>burp; belching; eructation</dd><br>
<dd>먹은 음식이 잘 소화되지 않아서 생긴 가스가 입으로 나옴. 또는 그 가스.</dd><br>
<dd>An act in which the gas created by food that has not digested well in one's stomach comes out through one's mouth; or such gas.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>트림하다 [트ː림하다]</dt><br>
<dd>burp; belch; eruct</dd><br>
<dd>먹은 음식이 잘 소화되지 않아서 생긴 가스가 입으로 나오다.</dd><br>
<dd>For the gas created by food that has not digested well in one's stomach to come out through one's mouth.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>